    "objectID": "index.html",
    "href": "index.html",
    "title": "Peter’s Pumpkin Patch",
    "section": "",
    "text": "Good evening! A slight change this year with a throwback from 2017 background on each page. A tribute to the Prince of Darkness. My theme this year is classic movie monsters from the ’30s and ’40s. There are eleven pumkins total. I might have to revist this theme, as I kept thinking of selections I missed (Vincent Price, Forbidden Planet, etc). My friends in Anacortes did a VERY impressive haunted house display this year, so the last one was for them. Enjoy, and Happy Halloween!!!"
